    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Ready-or-Not"><a href="#Ready-or-Not" class="headerlink" title="Ready or Not"></a>Ready or Not</h1><h2 id="折扣平台"><a href="#折扣平台" class="headerlink" title="折扣平台"></a>折扣平台</h2><a class="button " href='https://store.steampowered.com/app/1144200/' title='Steam'><i class='fa-brands fa-steam'></i> Steam</a>

<h2 id="折扣价格"><a href="#折扣价格" class="headerlink" title="折扣价格"></a>折扣价格</h2><p>新史低价格将<strong>加粗</strong>显示，详情请查看<a class="link"   href="https://steamdb.info/app/1144200/" >SteamDB</a></p>
<ul>
<li>原价：￥NaN（-0%）</li>
<li>史低：￥93.75（NaN%）</li>
<li><strong>新史低：￥</strong>（）</li>
</ul>
